
Cactus Code Thorn ID_Switch_EOS
Thorn Author(s)     : Wolfgang Kastaun <physik@fangwolg.de>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Wolfgang Kastaun <physik@fangwolg.de>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

Recompute pressure of initial data from the EOS used in evolution.
Optionally, recompute temperature from specific energy or the other way around.

